text: "Mamacita" is a song by British rapper Tinie Tempah. It was released on 8 July 2016, as the third single from his third studio album, Youth (2017). The song, produced by Bless Beats, features vocals from Nigerian singer Wizkid. ==Music video== The song's music video premiered on 4 July 2016, via Tempah's official YouTube channel.
